@startuml
autonumber
title 2.10.2.2 View Transaction List

actor User as U
participant "FE Layer" as Client
note over U, Client : User interacts through FE before backend calls
U -> Client : uses web app UI
participant "InventoryController" as Ctrl
participant "InventoryService" as Svc
participant "IInventoryRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Client -> Ctrl : GET /api/inventory/transactions\n(GetTransactionsFilterRequest)
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : GetTransactionsAsync(filter, ct)
activate Svc

Svc -> Repo : GetTransactionsPagedAsync(filter, ct)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT InventoryTransactions\nJOIN TypeLv, StatusLv, ExportReasonLv,\nSupplier, CreatedBy, ApprovedBy, Items\nWITH filters ORDER BY CreatedAt DESC
activate DB
DB --> Repo : result rows
deactivate DB
note right of Repo : Map to InventoryTransactionListDto\nwith ItemCount and TotalValue
Repo --> Svc : PagedResultDTO<InventoryTransactionListDto>
deactivate Repo

Svc --> Ctrl : PagedResultDTO<InventoryTransactionListDto>
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> Client : 200 ApiResponse<PagedResultDTO<InventoryTransactionListDto>>
deactivate Ctrl

Client -> U : displays transaction list with pagination
@enduml
